{"tid":2042971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"何啟明入勞福局，立法會就冇機會有兩個何啟明(九龍東工聯會&九龍西民協)了。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-05-30T06:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T11:30:38.000Z","uid":7439,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c20ad960b41bf38164eb57d303f6f9d9a0a4aa08","tid":2042971,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">何啟明 （1985年1月6日－）<br />\n工聯會成員，勞工及福利局副局長<br />\n前香港立法會議員（勞工界），落選觀塘區議會議員（栢雅 2012年&mdash;2019年）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/03/11/2400061_708c514eb47e9d1ccc96ebe336c5fb30.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F03%2F11%2F2400061_708c514eb47e9d1ccc96ebe336c5fb30.jpeg&h=74dce8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h4lksEhB_a0NWCkND9VgUFGxcaCxlZnhAMjw6XAlkNXcvPSpFPm0gLXUMNCB6OSwdODkmIXAPcHIoai5Abzsg/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h4lksEhB_a0NWCkND9VgUFGxcaCxlZnhAMjw6XAlkNXcvPSpFPm0gLXUMNCB6OSwdODkmIXAPcHIoai5Abzsg%2Fw644&h=ef65b3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">何啟明（1988年9月18日－）<br />\n民協副主席，深水埗區議員（南昌東 2016年&mdash;2023年）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/95501021_1644019692412062_763404009930227712_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=-1OiZh2DFkAAX-w7imQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=be3b4e3a7e6235790d7e0c2433a923e8&amp;oe=5EF96793\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F95501021_1644019692412062_763404009930227712_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D-1OiZh2DFkAAX-w7imQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Dbe3b4e3a7e6235790d7e0c2433a923e8%26oe%3D5EF96793&h=77710cd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f70961e619f990f89aabd3ad269b6ff5c0b7c33","tid":2042971,"uid":7439,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:11:14.000Z","msg":"何啟明 Ho Kai Ming Kalvin<br />\n46分鐘 &middot; <br />\n#企係工人對面嘅工賊會竟然可以做勞福局副局長<br />\n#選輸咗區議會被市民放棄嘅議員轉個身又可以加入政府<br />\n#好啦而家仲臨陣退縮放棄埋九東街坊<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#btw各位五毛小粉紅唔好like錯<br />\n#我係民協何啟明</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#五大訴求 #缺一不可<br />\n#光復香港 #時代革命"},{"pid":"961ab703337dc6ac8e6c88f01bd3fb13ee3559fe","tid":2042971,"uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"牙強咁撚好打，去超區拍琼子啦<br />\n乜乜羽返九東跟牙盛隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/95979475_1647890672024964_3333466651210285056_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=Hau46bbcUjgAX_alXxp&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=aa240523d4647d8ecfe1b28c992a6e9a&amp;oe=5EF766B7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F95979475_1647890672024964_3333466651210285056_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DHau46bbcUjgAX_alXxp%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Daa240523d4647d8ecfe1b28c992a6e9a%26oe%3D5EF766B7&h=75dc872b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"320d0937d326103500ecad411f4b50f4c2e05f4c","tid":2042971,"uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:16:02.000Z","msg":"民建聯劉國勳以去屆立法會選舉為例，指勞工界的工聯會何啟明及「超區」的民協何啟明如一同參與地區直選會出現「撞名」情況。工聯會麥美娟亦指何啟明（工聯會）對「撞名」十分困擾，「何啟明」即使身穿工聯會服裝仍會被當作民協何啟明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，認為刪去黨徽及人像影響選舉公平性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/157424/org/37abc2ffc9f1c99ba72ea1f2c2aad2e3.jpg/Dt-olTY68Obffp75jv4jalrtNjREdy6AjdS-BI3UvgQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F157424%2Forg%2F37abc2ffc9f1c99ba72ea1f2c2aad2e3.jpg%2FDt-olTY68Obffp75jv4jalrtNjREdy6AjdS-BI3UvgQ%3Fv%3D